---
import ServiceLayout from '@layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Family Pottery Painting Experience"
  description="Multi-generational pottery painting fun in Centerville, TN. Perfect family bonding activity with professional glazing and kiln-firing included."
  price="$15-25 per person"
  duration="1-2 hours"
  location="Centerville, TN"
  keywords="family pottery painting, kids pottery, family activities, Centerville"
>
  <section slot="overview">
    <h2>Family Pottery Painting Experience - Centerville, TN</h2>
    <p>Create beautiful memories together with our Family Pottery Painting Experience. Everyone selects a pre-made pottery piece and paints it their own way, creating unique keepsakes while bonding as a family.</p>

    <h3>The Experience</h3>
    <p>Our pottery painting is designed for families of all ages—from grandparents to toddlers. Each family member chooses a pre-made piece, and using our paints and supplies, creates their own unique design. No experience necessary! While you paint, our team creates a fun, relaxed atmosphere perfect for bonding.</p>

    <h3>What's Included</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Pre-made pottery piece selection</li>
      <li>All painting supplies (paints, brushes, tools)</li>
      <li>Professional glazing and kiln-firing</li>
      <li>Friendly guidance from our staff</li>
      <li>Family-friendly environment</li>
      <li>Finished pieces shipped or picked up</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Perfect For</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Grandparent visits and bonding</li>
      <li>Birthday celebrations</li>
      <li>Family reunion activities</li>
      <li>Weekend family time</li>
      <li>Creating lasting keepsakes</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Age Groups</h3>
    <p>We welcome families with children ages 3+. Our setup is completely safe for young artists, and our staff knows how to make painting fun for all ages. Parents can enjoy our integrated café while kids paint!</p>

    <h3>Pricing</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Individual pieces: $5-15 each</li>
      <li>Family package (4 people): $50-80</li>
      <li>Group packages available</li>
    </ul>

    <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><strong>Book your family experience!</strong> Call (931) XXX-XXXX or email info@thelocalplace.com. Located at 111 South Public Square, Upstairs, Centerville, TN 37033.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="testimonials">
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Our family had such a wonderful time! The kids loved painting and our finished pieces are displayed proudly in our home."</em></p>
      <p><strong>The Johnson Family</strong> - Nashville (45 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Best grandparent bonding activity ever! The staff was so patient with our young grandkids. Worth the drive!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Grandma Joan & Grandpa Bill</strong> - Brentwood (40 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"My kids still talk about the day we all painted pottery together. These pieces mean so much to us!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Sarah K.</strong> - Franklin (35 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="related">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;">
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Kids Pottery Painting Class</h3>
        <p>Fun, age-appropriate pottery painting classes designed for children.</p>
        <a href="/art-studio/kids-pottery-painting-class" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Pottery and Candle Combo Session</h3>
        <p>Experience both pottery and candle making in one creative session.</p>
        <a href="/art-studio/pottery-and-candle-combo-session" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Kids Candle Making Class</h3>
        <p>Safe, fun candle-making experiences designed for children.</p>
        <a href="/art-studio/kids-candle-making-class" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServiceLayout>
